rows.label: tlk70000031_03_msg0002
rows.name:
You might not be lost causes after all,
mates.

rows.label: tlk70000031_03_msg0003
rows.name:
But that don't mean I want anything
to do with you.

rows.label: tlk70000031_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Go take on a few tasks from people,
build up a bit of a rep and maybe
I'll change my mind.

rows.label: tlk70000031_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Run along now, like good little
kiddywinks.
